| 4G>  3B<  1G>  2B<
sdr> as couples touch 1/4
| 3B^  3G^  4Gv  4Bv  2B^  2G^  1Gv  1Bv
sdr> /// note that 'head-ness' transfers to the couple:
sdr> as couples heads run
| 4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv  1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^
sdr> /// this currently doesn't parse:
sdr> ///    as couples as couples hinge
